[{"id":"e88f89bda503e6290d4e520ed224ecb5","from":"Learnist","from_email":"feedback@learni.st","to":"jeffrey","to_list":[{"name":"jeffrey","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Get the Learnist extension for Google Chrome!","date":"2015-02-17T23:41:05.000Z","formatted_date":"Feb 17, 2015","formatted_time":"11:41 PM","body":"Learnist | Share What You Know\nHi Jeffrey,\nThe Learnist Chrome extension is now live in the Chrome web store!\n\nChrome users can install the Learnist extension and add content to a board from anywhere on the web.\nDownload it here (https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/learnist/ibnplnfkcgplbcdebdiehppcdllgfklb?hl=en-US\u2277=US&utm_source=one_off&utm_medium=member_email&utm_campaign=extension_launch&utm_content=download_btn)\n\nAdd to your boards from around the web with a single click.\nhttp://learni.st/chrome_extension?utm_source=one_off&utm_medium=member_email&utm_campaign=extension_launch&utm_content=board_image\n\nWant to learn more? This great board (http://learni.st/users/Learnist.Content/boards/105511-how-to-use-the-chrome-extension-for-learnist?utm_source=one_off&utm_medium=member_email&utm_campaign=extension_launch&utm_content=link_text) has all you need to know about the new Chrome extension.\n\nCreate your own boards today.\n\nOn Learnist, we provide a platform that helps people share their knowledge. After all, the best way to learn is to teach others.\nShare your knowledge (http://learni.st/dashboard?utm_source=one_off&utm_medium=member_email&utm_campaign=extension_launch&utm_content=share_knowledge_btn)\n\nGet your Learnist board featured on our homepage and promoted in our emails. Click here (http://learni.st/users/shavers/boards/85499-how-to-get-featured-on-learnist?utm_source=one_off&utm_medium=member_email&utm_campaign=extension_launch&utm_content=link_text) to learn more.\n------------------------------------------------------------\n\nTry Learnist on your Android or iOS device\nhttps://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.learnist https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/learnist-worlds-knowledge/id826591175?mt=8&uo=4\n\nLearnist values your privacy and does not make your email address available to any other third party without your permission.\n\n\u00a9 2014, Learnist Inc. 500 3rd Street Suite 260, San Francisco, CA 94107\nunsubscribe from this list (http://learni.us5.list-manage.com/unsubscribe?u=e682d21f40f033c5e91fc1903&id=811eaba20a&e=77acee5fb9&c=dfd4dbd8f9) | update subscription preferences (http://learni.us5.list-manage1.com/profile?u=e682d21f40f033c5e91fc1903&id=811eaba20a&e=77acee5fb9) | view email in browser (http://us5.campaign-archive2.com/?u=e682d21f40f033c5e91fc1903&id=dfd4dbd8f9&e=77acee5fb9)","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n<head style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n  <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width\" style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n  \n  <style type=\"text/css\" style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n\t\t*{\n\t\t\tmargin:0;\n\t\t\tpadding:0;\n\t\t\tfont-family:\"Helvetica Neue\", \"Helvetica\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n\t\t}\n\t\timg{\n\t\t\tmax-width:100%;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.collapse{\n\t\t\tmargin:0;\n\t\t\tpadding:0;\n\t\t}\n\t\thr{\n\t\t\twidth:100%;\n\t\t\theight:1px;\n\t\t\tmargin:0 auto 10px;\n